description: Bespoke Extracts, Inc. provides hemp-derived cannabidiol (CBD) products. The company offers CBD formulations, including manuka honey and in the form of lotions and balms; and markets CBD extracts in capsule form, topicals, and gummies. It offers its products through its direct to consumers e-commerce store bespokeextracts.com. The company was formerly known as DiMi Telematics International, Inc. and changed its name to Bespoke Extracts, Inc. in March 2017. The company is headquartered in Denver, Colorado.
